<i>adjective</i>: 매운, 맵다 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>매운</dt><br>
<dd>having an agreeably pungent taste</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: savory, savoury, piquant, spicy, zesty</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>맵다</dt><br>
<dd>producing a burning sensation on the taste nerves</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: hot, spicy, piquant, tangy</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
